ervice`和`checkoutservice`级联延迟。\n\n3. **影响范围**：整个购物流程的关键路径都受到影响，包括下单、支付、配送、购物车操作等核心功能。\n\n4. **网络vs服务问题**：由于多个服务都出现延迟，且延迟倍数较高，这更可能是下游服务（redis）性能问题，而非网络问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to severe performance degradation causing excessive memory usage on aiops-k8s-08 node"}
