ervice：85.0秒（正常18.2秒）\n\n2. **根因定位**：根据调用链拓扑，`redis`是`cartservice`的下游依赖，而`cartservice`的redis访问延迟异常严重（15.1倍），这表明**redis可能是根因**，导致`cartservice`和`checkoutservice`级联延迟。\n\n3. **影响范围**：整个购物流程的关键路径都受到影响，包括下单、支付、配送、购物车操作等核心功能。\n\n4. **网络vs服务问题**：由于多个服务都出现延迟，且延迟倍数较高，这更可能是下游服务（redis）性能问题，而非网络问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "d4cf6596-245", "component": "redis-cart-0", "reason": "redis HGET and HMSET rrt_max spike causing cartservice latency cascade", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "TraceAnalysis(d4cf6596-245)", "observation": "redis HGET latency increased from 1.8s to 26.7s (15.1x), HMSET from 1.6s to 7.3s (4.6x)"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(redis-cart-0)", "observation": "pod_cpu_usage anomaly but node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes dropped 3.8GB on aiops-k8s-08"}, {"step": 3, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "redis-cart-0 located on aiops-k8s-08 with cartservice-2, both showing rrt_max anomalies"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
